sequenceDiagram
    participant User as User/Notebook
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.3
    participant Webhook as Webhook Service<br/>9443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+
    participant Controller as RayCluster Controller
    participant RouteAPI as Route API (OpenShift)<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS
    participant OAuthProxy as OAuth Proxy<br/>443/TCP HTTPS edge
    participant RayDashboard as Ray Dashboard<br/>8265/TCP HTTP
    participant Client as Ray Client
    participant RayHead as Ray Head Pod<br/>10001/TCP gRPC mTLS
    participant Kueue as Kueue Controller
    participant AppWrapCtrl as AppWrapper Controller
    participant Prometheus as Prometheus

    Note over User,RayDashboard: Flow 1: RayCluster Creation with OAuth (OpenShift)

    User->>K8sAPI: POST RayCluster CR<br/>Auth: Bearer Token (ServiceAccount)
    K8sAPI->>Webhook: Validate/Mutate RayCluster<br/>mTLS (API Server)
    Webhook-->>K8sAPI: Admission Response
    K8sAPI-->>User: Created

    Controller->>K8sAPI: Watch RayCluster<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
    Controller->>RouteAPI: Create Route (ray-dashboard-*)<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
    Controller->>K8sAPI: Create Service<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
    Controller->>K8sAPI: Create NetworkPolicy<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
    Controller->>K8sAPI: Create Secrets (CA, TLS)<br/>Auth: Bearer Token

    User->>OAuthProxy: GET /dashboard<br/>Auth: OAuth Bearer Token
    OAuthProxy->>RayDashboard: Forward (internal pod)<br/>No encryption
    RayDashboard-->>OAuthProxy: Dashboard UI
    OAuthProxy-->>User: HTTPS Response

    Note over User,AppWrapCtrl: Flow 2: AppWrapper Scheduling with Kueue

    User->>K8sAPI: POST AppWrapper CR<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
    K8sAPI->>Webhook: Validate AppWrapper<br/>mTLS
    Webhook-->>K8sAPI: Admission Response

    Kueue->>K8sAPI: Update AppWrapper status<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount token
    AppWrapCtrl->>K8sAPI: Watch AppWrapper status<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount token
    AppWrapCtrl->>K8sAPI: Create wrapped resources<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount token

    Note over Client,RayHead: Flow 3: Ray Client Connection with mTLS

    Client->>RouteAPI: Connect to ray-client-*<br/>443/TCP HTTPS<br/>Client Certificate
    RouteAPI->>RayHead: Passthrough to 10001/TCP<br/>gRPC mTLS<br/>Client Certificate
    RayHead-->>Client: Ray API Response

    Note over Prometheus,Controller: Flow 4: Metrics Collection

    Prometheus->>Controller: GET /metrics<br/>8080/TCP HTTP<br/>Auth: Bearer Token (ServiceAccount)
    Controller-->>Prometheus: Prometheus metrics
